{
  "id": "adv_main_03_01_02",
  "title": "BIG4編1章2話",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_tension-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "三枝信司",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shinji",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "うちに――星見プロに入らないか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "How about joining us - Hoshimi Productions?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_01_02/sud_vo_adv_main_03_01_02-kan001.m4a",
      "text": "……はぁ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Huh?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 5.3347165902,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_01_02/sud_vo_adv_main_03_01_02-kor001.m4a",
      "text": "どういうつもりですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What do you mean?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 7.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_01_02/sud_vo_adv_main_03_01_02-kor002.m4a",
      "text": "確かに私達は、プレタポルテを離れて\nフリーになったけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's true that we've left Pret-a-Porter\nand become freelancers‚ but…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 12.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_01_02/sud_vo_adv_main_03_01_02-mhk001.m4a",
      "text": "三枝さん、貴方が業界を代表する\n名プロデューサーであることは存じています",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Mr. Saegusa‚ I know you're a renowned producer\nrepresenting the industry",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 18.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_01_02/sud_vo_adv_main_03_01_02-mhk002.m4a",
      "text": "ですが……これは、お互いにとって\nいい方法とは思えません",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But… I don't think this is\na good solution for either of us",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 24,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_01_02/sud_vo_adv_main_03_01_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "（俺も同意見だ。スリクスは不正に関与していないが）\n（姫野さんと共に星見プロを苦しめた相手でもある）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(I agree. Although IIIX wasn't involved in the fraud)\n(They were still opponents who caused trouble for Hoshimi Pro along with Himeno-san)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 31,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "三枝信司",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shinji",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "だからこそ、君達を誘うんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's exactly why I'm inviting you",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 34.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "三枝信司",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shinji",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "今回の一件で、遺恨を残したくない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I don't want to leave any grudges from this incident",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 37.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_01_02/sud_vo_adv_main_03_01_02-kor003.m4a",
      "text": "遺恨……ですか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Grudges… you say?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 41.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "三枝信司",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shinji",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "今回の事件は、我々事務所……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This incident is a problem of our agency…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 43.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "三枝信司",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shinji",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "もっと言えば、アイドル業界全体の問題だ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "or rather‚ the entire idol industry",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 46.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "三枝信司",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shinji",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "むしろ、現場のアイドル達には迷惑を掛けてしまった",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If anything‚ we've caused trouble for the idols on the ground",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 51.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "三枝信司",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shinji",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "だからその償いをさせてほしい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So I want to make amends for that",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 55.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_01_02/sud_vo_adv_main_03_01_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "（三枝さん、そんな風に考えていたのか。だけど……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(Mr. Saegusa‚ so that's what you were thinking. But still…)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 58.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_01_02/sud_vo_adv_main_03_01_02-mhk003.m4a",
      "text": "お気持ちは嬉しく思います",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I appreciate your sentiment",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 64.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_01_02/sud_vo_adv_main_03_01_02-mhk004.m4a",
      "text": "ですが、私達が何をしようとしていたか――\n忘れた訳ではないでしょう？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But you haven't forgotten what we were trying to do…\nHave you?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 71.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 74.5666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 74.5666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_contact-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 74.8
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_01_02/sud_vo_adv_main_03_01_02-mhk005.m4a",
      "text": "私達は祭典で優勝した後、長瀬麻奈の楽曲全てを奪う",
      "translations": {
        "en": "After winning the festival‚ we were going to take all of Nagase Mana's songs",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 75.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 82
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_01_02/sud_vo_adv_main_03_01_02-kor004.m4a",
      "text": "具体的にはプレタポルテの資金と人脈で\n楽曲の権利を押さえるそうよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Specifically‚ we were going to use Pret-a-Porter's funds and connections\nto secure the rights to the songs",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 85.8343333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_01_02/sud_vo_adv_main_03_01_02-kan002.m4a",
      "text": "それで長瀬麻奈の歌をこの世の中から\nファンの記憶からも消しちゃうんだって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And then erase Nagase Mana's songs from this world\nand from the fans' memories too",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 93.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_01_02/sud_vo_adv_main_03_01_02-kan003.m4a",
      "text": "きゃはは！　mihoちゃんって容赦ないよね～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Kyahaha! miho-chan is so merciless~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 97.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 97.5333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 102.7
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_01_02/sud_vo_adv_main_03_01_02-kor005.m4a",
      "text": "やがて長瀬麻奈が生きていたという証はなくなる\n私達の上には誰もいらない。そこはmihoと同意見よ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eventually‚ all proof that Nagase Mana ever lived would disappear\nWe don't need anyone above us. I agree with miho on that",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 108.0433333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 113.4666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_01_02/sud_vo_adv_main_03_01_02-kor006.m4a",
      "text": "スリクスはアイドルの頂点に立ち\n私達はその後それぞれの夢を叶える",
      "translations": {
        "en": "IIIX would stand at the top of the idol world\nand after that‚ we'd each fulfill our own dreams",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 118.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 123.1333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_serious-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 123.3666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_01_02/sud_vo_adv_main_03_01_02-kan004.m4a",
      "text": "ていうか、もしkana達がいいって言ってもさ\n星見プロの子達だって絶対嫌でしょ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I mean‚ even if we said yes\nthe Hoshimi Pro kids would definitely hate it‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 128.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_01_02/sud_vo_adv_main_03_01_02-kan005.m4a",
      "text": "ほら、そっちの人も",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Look‚ that person over there too",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 131.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "三枝信司",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shinji",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "……だそうだが",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…So that's how it is",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 134.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "三枝信司",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shinji",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "{user}、お前はどう思う？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}‚ what do you think?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 136.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_01_02/sud_vo_adv_main_03_01_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "俺は――許せません",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I… can't forgive this",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 138.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_01_02/sud_vo_adv_main_03_01_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "麻奈の歌を奪い、麻奈の存在を消し去ろうとしたことは\nどんな事情があったとしても、絶対に許せない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Trying to steal Mana's songs and erase her existence\nNo matter what the circumstances‚ I absolutely can't forgive that",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 146.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_01_02/sud_vo_adv_main_03_01_02-mhk006.m4a",
      "text": "……当然ですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…As expected",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 150.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_01_02/sud_vo_adv_main_03_01_02-mhk007.m4a",
      "text": "それに……私の考えは今も変わってませんから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Besides… my thoughts haven't changed even now",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 152.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_01_02/sud_vo_adv_main_03_01_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "（なぜここまで麻奈のことを……理由は分からない）\n（でも、スリクスにはスリクスの事情があるんだろう）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(Why go this far about Mana… I don't understand the reason)\n(But IIIX must have their own circumstances)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 162.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
